name: Stranded? Only Time Will Tell
description:
Oh no! You may get stranded trying to navigate through the maze. Do not despair! Wait 10 seconds and you may find another path to appear.

Controls are arrow keys or wasd (implemented using an USA QWERTY keyboard).  ESC will quit the game (originally a Windows game), but this is HTML which will cause your game to be stuck forever. There is no sound or music.

This game was created with the theme of "every 10 seconds" for Ludum Dare 51 jam.
